snippet.title: Johnny Depp accuses ex-wife Amber Heard of lying in UK libel case | ABC News
snippet.description:
Depp, the 57-year-old Pirates of the Caribbean star, is suing the publisher of UK tabloid newspaper The Sun for libel over an article in April 2018 calling Depp a "wife beater".
